Simple-Processor-9-vhdl-cisc is a simpler secuential processor for academic 
and teaching purpose write in VHDL. The ISA consists of four CISC
instructions MV, MVI, ADD and SUB. Architecture
is Register-Register.

The design has been simulated with ModelSimÂ®.